{"hash":"9f2d0d44c300e4d1821a2acaadb3f49cdeba69f7","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"af61344729ec8c01571d4145b0e48d78","title":"How to use ThreeFold Now","description":"","path":"/docs/how-threefold-now/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h1 id=\"how-to-use-threefold-now\"><a href=\"#how-to-use-threefold-now\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>How to use ThreeFold Now</h1>\n<h2 id=\"first-visit-the-threefold-now-marketplace\"><a href=\"#first-visit-the-threefold-now-marketplace\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>First, visit the <a href=\"https://marketplace.threefold.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ThreeFold Now Marketplace</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You'll see solutions organized into various categories.</li>\n<li>Simply choose the solution you want to launch from the menu.</li>\n<li>You'll need to log in through ThreeFold Connect, an authenticator for the ThreeFold Now Marketplace.</li>\n<li>You can find more on ThreeFold Connect <a href=\"https://manual.threefold.io/#/3botconnect_install\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. &#x3C;&#x3C;&#x3C; CHANGE THIS!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"next-use-the-guided-setup-to-create-your-solution\"><a href=\"#next-use-the-guided-setup-to-create-your-solution\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Next, use the guided setup to create your solution</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Each solution has its own flow â€“ actions in order to deploy your own instance on top of the ThreeFold Grid.</li>\n<li>If you're feeling lost, each live tool has a tutorial on its page here on the wiki.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"where-to-ask-questions\"><a href=\"#where-to-ask-questions\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Where to ask questions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Feel free to ask us any questions you might have on <a href=\"https://forum.threefold.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">our forum</a> in the feedback category.</li>\n<li>We also have a Telegram Group for TF Grid testers <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/BwOvOxxgK59GmRoZ2_sM0w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Please keep in mind that ThreeFold Now is currently running on testnet. Some of the first solutions will be coming to mainnet in December.</em></p>\n<p><em>Please forgive any instability you might encounter while our developers continue to work to bring you the best solutions possible and keep in mind the forum (linked directly above) is there for you to bring questions or report any issues.</em></p>\n<p><em>As we are operating in demo mode, your deployments will be automatically be cancelled after three hours once you have had a chance to see what is possible.</em></p>\n","sidebar":"docs","next":"/docs/tfgrid/","prev":"/docs/why-threefold-now/","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"How to use ThreeFold Now","anchor":"#how-to-use-threefold-now"},{"depth":2,"value":"First, visit the ","anchor":"https://marketplace.threefold.io"},{"depth":2,"value":"Next, use the guided setup to create your solution","anchor":"#next-use-the-guided-setup-to-create-your-solution"},{"depth":2,"value":"Where to ask questions","anchor":"#where-to-ask-questions"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/docs/zeroci/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/wiki-publisher/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/wiki-publisher/","title":"Wiki Publisher"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/virtual-spaces/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/video-sharing/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/video-conf/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/tomochain/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/tfgrid/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/serverless/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/publishing-tool/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/upcoming-projects/","title":"Coming Up!"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/index/img/readme/","title":""}},{"n